      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolutely mint condition and has been meticulously cared for since day one. It looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor, with a flawless exterior finish and a pristine interior that still smells new. Mechanically, the car is perfect; the engine is incredibly responsive, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and every electronic feature functions exactly as intended. This is a rare find for a collector or anyone seeking a top-tier vehicle with zero compromises and a complete service history.",
